#. open this dir as project in eclipse
#. all jar files are in lib/ dir
#. configure the buildpath with el-api.jar, jsp-api.jar, servlet-api.jar, java-json.jar
#. create a new tomcat 8.5 server
#. add all the jars in lib/ dir to bootstrap of tomcat server
#. ./src/org/littletwitter/littletwitter/servlets/DBHandler.java contains db credential fields
#. create.sql re-sets the tables
#. data.sql adds some sample data
#. run server